{
  "stem": "10478.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then, of course, the, the empty places had  to filled with unemployed people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that way there was full employment going  on, yeah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lots of new laws came into effect, in a way, yeah, set up by Seyss-Inquart, who was the, the man who governed Holland on behalf of Hitler.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Seyss-Inquart.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, you ask me to do this?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Austria.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was an Austrian, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was a law of gatherings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not allowed to have big gatherings anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The, the curfew, of course, was one of the laws.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there was a whole bunch of new, new laws you had to, to, to try to-- and we were-- we had to hand in our radios, you know.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're not allowed to listen to the broadcasts from either England or America.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we only listen-- were allowed to listen to the German broadcast.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were afraid we were going to read-- going to hear the truth of what was really going to happen.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were only just allowed to listen to German propaganda.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what they did, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not, not right away, but later on, when we all were required to have an ID card with a picture and a fingerprint on that, then they put on the ID cards, with the Jewish, a black J.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So anytime they was  in control, they could, right away, see that man is a Jew.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, of course, they picked up some Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was something around sabotage or whatever they are.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's the Jews' act.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they picked up some Jewish men in, in, in Maastricht or in other places, and sent them to camp, yeah.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember one case, one man was, for a reason, arrested by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
